never was good with the planning stuff...","actor":305023},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":-1,"say":"But, it'd be a shame to not go to the banquet after going through all that trouble to find a dress...","actor":305023},{"actorName":"{namecode:97}","bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":2,"dir":1,"say":"The only thing that matters to me is Commander. Other things aren't of any concern to me.","actor":307071},{"actorName":"{namecode:97}","bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Or rather, that's what I thought at first... Honestly, this fleet... feels like home.","actor":307071},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":-1,"say":"Ehehe~ It's a home made by Milord, after all!","actor":305023},{"actorName":"{namecode:97}","bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":2,"dir":1,"say":"Yamashiro, did you go to any events?","actor":307071},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":2,"dir":-1,"say":"Me? Um, I suppose I've been helping Fusou this whole time... Oh, and I went on a test of courage with some of the destroyers...","actor":305023},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":1,"action":[{"number":2,"x":0,"type":"shake","delay":0.8,"dur":0.1,"y":60}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":-1,"say":"That was so scary... I'm getting the shakes just thinking about it...","actor":305023},{"actorName":"{namecode:97}","bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Hehe, sounds like you had a good time. I'll have to join in myself the next time around.","actor":307071},{"actorName":"{namecode:97}","bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":2,"dir":1,"say":"But by the looks of things, Commander won't be done for a while...","actor":307071},{"actorName":"{namecode:97}","bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"say":"Yamashiro, care for a drink?","paintingFadeOut":{"time":0.5,"side":2},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","actor":307071},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"action":[{"number":2,"x":0,"type":"shake","delay":0.2,"dur":0.2,"y":60}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":-1,"say":"Um, sake?! Fusou said it'd be best for me not to drink... but I've always been a little curious!","actor":305023},{"actorName":"{namecode:97}","bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":3,"dir":1,"say":"Hehe. This stuff isn't very strong, so you should be fine...","actor":307071},{"actorName":"{namecode:97}","bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"blackBg":true,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Here, come sit next to me. Until Commander is finished with work, let's have some girl's talk.","actor":307071}]}